# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __neg__, __pos__, __abs__ across all 5 pathlib subjects
#
# 5 classes x 3 methods = 15 rows.
# All values are false; pathlib defines no unary negation, unary plus, or
# abs() operators. Path objects are filesystem path abstractions; unary
# arithmetic operators are not part of the path protocol.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

